# ğŸ“ Task Manager

This is a simple command-line Task Manager written in Python.  
It allows you to create, view, mark as completed, and delete tasks.  
The tasks are saved in a local JSON file (`tasks.json`) to persist between sessions.

## ğŸ“Œ Features

- View all your tasks with their statuses.
- Add new tasks.
- Mark tasks as done.
- Remove tasks.
- Persistent storage using JSON.

